Definition: a security created when a group of mortgages are gathered together and bonds are sold to other institutions or the public
Example: investors receive a portion of the interest payments on the mortgages as well as the principal payments; usually guaranteed by the government
Synonyms: security, a, created, when, group, of, mortgages, are, gathered, together, and, bonds, sold, to, other, institutions, or, the, public, investors, receive, portion, interest, payments, on, as, well, principal, usually, guaranteed, by, government
Category: noun.possession
